| 10 | INSERT INTO t1 VALUES(15,25*4)   | AE06BCEB7FDFE5E7BF260DB315B7F7E0 | INSERT INTO T1 VALUES ( ? , ? * ? )  | INSERT 语句                        |
| 2  | DELETE FROM t1 WHERE c1 = "whh"  | A66D5C4325D82467E443039AAED826F1 | DELETE FROM T1 WHERE C1 = ?          | DELETE 语句                        |
