|  1 | INSERT INTO t1 VALUES(15,25)    | 0896093076902A887B06E3329D9AF69E | INSERT INTO T1 VALUES ( ? , ? )  | INSERT 语句   |
|  2 | DELETE FROM t1 WHERE c1 = "whh" | A66D5C4325D82467E443039AAED826F1 | DELETE FROM T1 WHERE C1 = ?      | DELETE 语句   |
|  3 | UPDATE t1 SET id = id + 1       | 83091A9F378BA243C82A390F5F7BBB77 | UPDATE T1 SET ID = ID + ?        | UPDATE 语句   |
