|  4 | DELETE FROM t1 WHERE c1 LIKE "%W%"                      | A66D5C4325D82467E443039AAED826F1 | DELETE FROM T1 WHERE C1 LIKE ?   | DELETE 语句   |
|  5 | UPDATE t1 SET id = id * 1                               | 83091A9F378BA243C82A390F5F7BBB77 | UPDATE T1 SET ID = ID + ?        | UPDATE 语句   |
|  6 | SELECT * FROM tl WHERE id < 20                          | F7A3D808C12C7E7E2392FCE142467F9D | SELECT * FROM TL WHERE ID < ?    | SELECT 语句   |
